<r-cell
    class="b-lb work--title-intro"
    span="1-2"
    span-s="row"
    span-lg="row"
>
	<div class="b-b work--section-title">
		<small aria-hidden="true">Skills</small>
	</div>
</r-cell>

<r-cell class="b-lrb skills" span="3-12" span-s="row" span-lg="row">
	<span class="block b-b u-desktop-only"></span>
	<div class="skills--content">
		<div class="title">
			<h2 text-split letters-slide-up>I can help you with</h2>

			<p class="subtitle">
               From end-to-end product design to icon design. My focus is in achieving a balance between driving impactful business goals and delivering exceptional user experiences. I also have a knack for crafting visual languages that resonate with users.
            </p>
		</div>

		<ul>
			{% for skill in skills %}
				<li>
					<h3>{{ skill }}</h3>
				</li>
			{% endfor %}
		</ul>
	</div>
</r-cell>